<li> Fixed players being able to trigger a screen shake on other players</li> <li> Fixed Shift-F1 debug panel being accessible when cheats are disabled</li> <li> Fixed server browser not being displayed</li> <li> Improved refresh rate selection behavior</li> </ul>
