<p>An update to Counter-Strike: Source has just been released. Steam will update itself automatically when you restart. Here is a list of the changes:<br/><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><b>COUNTER-STRIKE: SOURCE CHANGES / ADDITIONS:</b><br/><li>Fixed various name changing exploit crashes</li></ul></p>
