(240, '2005-07-20', 'Counter-strike: Source Update Available', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_429\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>An update to Counter-Strike: Source has been released. The update will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Counter-Strike: Source</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Optimized game to lower CPU usage</li></ul></p>
